<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1270785>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Schematic drawings of Tetra aparinea n. sp.: 1. Dorsal view; 2. Female coxae and external genitalia; 3. Leg I; 4. Leg II; 5. Lateral view of annuli; 6. Internal view of female genitalia; 7. Empodium; 8. External view of male genitalia. Scale bar: 10 µm for 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 µm for 7." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1270785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

